channel.title: Nobody can get on my sevrver :S
channel.description:
Hey, i have a 562 yh, i have done port forwarding with utorrent on canyouseeme.org it can find me on port 43594 i have got no-ip.org andn nobody only me can logon to my server help me please
Thanks Shaun.

item.description:
@scipyo wrote:

I had the same problem with a 317 but this worked for me idk if it would work for you.
Do 562’s have a GUI file if so you might want to put you No-Ip in there then compile your server and either have your friends do the same or let them redownload it. Hope it works for you
